{
  "stem": "18281.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 131.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I had told you how we broke into our little house and got some valuables and some, some clothing out of there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I-- by night, we walked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's very dangerous to walk back to my uncle's house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Next day, I told my sister to stay where she was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was visiting an aunt in the countryside.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And from there and then, with the help of Belgium friends, I obtained a place for her in the convent school of Waterloo, the famous Waterloo of the battle and Napoleon.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she checked in there as a student and survived the rest of the, the war in that convent, even though part of the convent was occupied by German troops.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I myself with the help, again, of Belgian resistance and underground, was told to take a certain street car.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Belgium in those days was crisscrossed by what's called in Flemish a [FLEMISH], a farmer's train.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it really was a, an electrical street car that operated like a train and went from village to village.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they said-- they told me to take that street car to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I really wouldn't recall that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I tried to, to remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But probably, the landlady that rented us the little house that was instrumental in getting my sister-- she was friends with the Mother Superior-- getting my sister into the convent school.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She probably gave me some names.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I really don't recall.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I do know I got strict instructions to hold my suitcase in the same hand with the German edition of a type of magazine.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was called And it had all the battles and all the victories of the Germans in there with lots of pictures.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I did that.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
